S.FORM: United States Gaga kska Daya Meycow ka United states, 38 00 N, 97 00 W ka gaga na nniqan. Kana ka knlbangan na o 9,833,517 sq km(hangan na o Tg3) (knlbanga dxgal o 9,147,593 sq km, knlbangan qsiya o 685,924 sq km). Kana ka sejiqun o niqan 323,995,528 hiyi. Gaga Washington, DC ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 4 idas 7 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. Manu ka dxgal United states ga wada sugan 44.50 ka dxgal qpahan, 33.30 ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 22.20 na. Bukung klwaan ta sayang o kiya ka Donald John Trump, pnaah hngkawas2017 idas 1 jiyax 20pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
